{"title" : "户外拓展" ,"content":"<P class=MsoNormal style='BACKGROUND: white; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 24pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly'><SPAN lang=ZH-CN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial'>户外拓展训练是模拟军事管理训练而衍生出来的一种培训项目，户外拓展培训是指利用自然地域（山川湖海）、通过模拟探险式情景结合为团队精心设计的拓展设施，达成解决或促进团队执行力、协作、领导力等</SPAN><SPAN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial'><?xml:namespace prefix = 'o' ns = 'urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office' /><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P><P class=MsoNormal style='BACKGROUND: white; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 24pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly'><SPAN lang=ZH-CN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial'>青少年户外拓展从根本上，需要满足青少年的成长需求，拓展精神与方式要与青少年成长目标相一致。金牌拓展团队建立于人力资源管理从业经验基础之上，所以在为青少年拓展项目设计时，融入了一定未来职业教育的部分，让孩子们从小懂得团队与协作的力量！</SPAN><SPAN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial'><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P><P class=MsoNormal style='BACKGROUND: white; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 24pt; TEXT-INDENT: 30pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.5'><SPAN lang=ZH-CN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial'>金牌户外拓展与众合作伙伴共同为企业推出四种类型户外拓展场地：</SPAN><SPAN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial'><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P><P class=MsoNormal style='BACKGROUND: white; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 72pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 24pt; TEXT-INDENT: -72pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: -6.0'><SPAN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial'>1<SPAN lang=ZH-CN>、山地拓展：在高山之上，设置拓展设施、营房、碉堡、</SPAN>CS<SPAN lang=ZH-CN>，同时让员工在天然氧吧中，感受大山的巍峨。</SPAN><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P><P class=MsoNormal style='BACKGROUND: white; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 72pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 24pt; TEXT-INDENT: -72pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: -6.0'><SPAN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial'>2<SPAN lang=ZH-CN>、海滩拓展：在大海之畔，设置拓展设施、营房、沙滩休闲设施，同时让员工在大海的涛声中，感受大海的情怀。</SPAN><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P><P class=MsoNormal style='BACKGROUND: white; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 72pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 24pt; TEXT-INDENT: -72pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: -6.0'><SPAN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial'>3<SPAN lang=ZH-CN>、军营拓展：在部队培训基地，设置拓展设施、营房、拉练穿越等，同时让员工感受军营的严谨风气与军人崇高的奉献精神。</SPAN><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P><P class=MsoNormal style='BACKGROUND: white; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 72pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 24pt; TEXT-INDENT: -72pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: -6.0'><SPAN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial'>4<SPAN lang=ZH-CN>、运动拓展：在铺有绿荫的塑胶运动场，进行一场别开生面的拓展活动或趣味运动会，无需远足即可感受团队协作的快乐。</SPAN><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P><P class=MsoNormal style='BACKGROUND: white; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 72pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 24pt; TEXT-INDENT: -72pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: -6.0'><SPAN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></SPAN></P><P class=MsoNormal style='LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 24pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-layout-grid-align: none'><SPAN lang=ZH-CN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312'>报名参加办法：</SPAN><SPAN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312'><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P><P class=MsoNormal style='LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 24pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-layout-grid-align: none'><SPAN lang=ZH-CN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312'>本项目以学校等青少年团体单位为主，提前一周电话咨询。</SPAN><SPAN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312'><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>"}